(15038, 1172, 'wpcf-right-video-image', 'https://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Conquer-The-East-Carbon-Fiber-Sunglasses-4-of-11.jpg'),
(15039, 1172, 'wpcf-text-under-right-video-image', '"We want to hopefully encourage others to just do what they are aching to do. It doesn''t take much more than the will to do it. We are all capable of the same things. "'),
