(689, 1, '2015-12-07 02:36:42', '2015-12-07 02:36:42', '<div id="content-about">\n<div class="col1">\n\n&nbsp;\n\nThe first full frame carbon fiber sunglass collection in the world. 6 years from concept to market.\n\nIn all of its complexities, carbon fiber has its own life. It will not bend to the will of the hands that shape it like metal, plastic, or acetate would. At best, it will parlay before a true trimester and artisan; then unwillingly surrender to creation. With three patents pending on the design that makes Dirocco unique where other companies have failed, our product is truly unique in the world.\n\n</div>\nAny divergence and slight differences are due to the artisanal production of this item. They are not to be considered imperfections, but like all creation, birthmarks that make them unique.\n<div class="col2"></div>\n</div>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '115-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-12-07 02:36:42', '2015-12-07 02:36:42', '', 115, 'http://dev.hungrylemur.com/115-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
