(18, 158, '2015-01-27 17:54:48', '2015-01-27 17:54:48', '<div class="body-journal">\r\n<div class="journal-content">\r\n<p class="journal-inner"><span class="drop-cap">I</span>t comes in at least once a year. The token NYC blizzard.\r\nBut last night we saw the opportunity to have a little fun. So we took our Burton snowboards and did what we could with the small slopes of Riverside Park.</p>\r\n<p class="journal-inner">It was eery to see the city without a single car out. Total silence everywhere. It was almost therapeutic. We walked down the west side highway in total solitude. Good times.\r\nMake the most out of every night.\r\n– Sebastian.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'NYC: LIGHTS OUT', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nyc-blizzard', '', '', '2016-02-24 20:18:14', '2016-02-24 20:18:14', '', 0, 'http://dev.hungrylemur.com/?p=18', 0, 'post', '', 0),
