(137, 1, '2015-09-10 20:39:55', '2015-09-10 20:39:55', 'ARTISANRY\r\nWhen creating your DiRocco frame, a lot of precise methods are used. Laser cutting being at the top. However, a large portion of the process involves handcrafting which results in no two pairs of DiRocco frames to be identical. Therefore, any divergence and slight differences are due to the artisinal production of the fine pieces. They are not to be considered imperfections, but like all creation, birthmarks that make them unique.', 'Product Artisanry', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'product-artisanry', '', '', '2015-12-10 22:50:27', '2015-12-10 22:50:27', '', 0, 'http://dev.hungrylemur.com/?page_id=137', 0, 'page', '', 0),
