(175, 158, '2015-09-12 19:49:58', '2015-09-12 19:49:58', '<div class="post-single-bottom">The DiRocco Team share the story that lead them to this point.</div>\r\n<div class="post-single-bottom"></div>\r\n<div class="post-single-bottom"></div>\r\n<div class="post-single-bottom">“It’s not about owning something vintage, or something new. I have nothing\r\nagainst new bikes. It’s about owning something special. The library of new\r\nis limited by time; but the past is vast and for the taking.”</div>\r\n[KGVID poster="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/video-image_03.png" fullwidth="true" caption="Cleaning the wrench" endofvideooverlay="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/video-image_03.png"]http://media.w3.org/2010/05/sintel/trailer.mp4[/KGVID]\r\n\r\n[gallery columns="2" size="full" link="none" ids="64,65"]\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/video-image_03.png" alt="“a”" width="649" height="433" />', 'Carbon', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'taming', '', '', '2015-12-15 01:02:16', '2015-12-15 01:02:16', '', 0, 'http://dev.hungrylemur.com/?p=175', 0, 'post', '', 0),
