(1117, 161, '2016-02-17 17:48:43', '2016-02-17 17:48:43', '<div id="content-about">\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/BOX_INSIDE_.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-421 aligncenter" src="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/BOX_INSIDE_.jpg" alt="BOX_INSIDE_" width="600" height="500" /></a>\r\n<div class="col1">\r\n\r\nAfter over five years investing into the research and development to create our frames; we sought to test the market in some of the most prestigious eyewear boutiques in the country and around the world.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col1"></div>\r\n<div class="col1">What we found was both rewarding and frustrating. The boutiques priced and sold our collection as high as $1400 per piece. It was a massive compliment to the work we had accomplished. Unfortunately, it effectively made them obtainable for a very select few.</div>\r\n<div class="col1"></div>\r\n<div class="col1">We seek to be exclusively inclusive. And, in this era, going direct to consumer is something that will benefit all those who have a sense of style and not just a fat wallet. After all, we only manufacture 500 units of each frame per year.</div>\r\n<div class="col1"></div>\r\n<div id="content-about"></div>', 'Stockists', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '115-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-17 17:48:43', '2016-02-17 17:48:43', '', 115, 'https://www.diroccoeyewear.com/115-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
