d so, is why we are sharing his long journeyed story on our featured storytellers section.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0em 0px 1.76471em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: 1.76471em; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: baseline;">The pictures were taken by photographer @GlenAllsop</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="medium body-copy" style="margin: 0px 139.984375px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: WhitneyLight, WhitneyBook Times, serif; line-height: inherit; font-size: 17px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 679.984375px; float: left; color: #2b2b2b; letter-spacing: 0.23999999463558197px;"></div>\r\n<div class="medium body-copy" style="margin: 0px 139.984375px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: WhitneyLight, WhitneyBook, Times, serif; line-height: inherit; font-size: 17px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 679.984375px; float: left; color: #2b2b2b; letter-spacing: 0.23999999463558197px;"></div>\r\n<a href="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/CAFE-RACER-MOTO-glen-allsop-010.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-737" src="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/CAFE-RACER-MOTO-glen-allsop-010.jpg" alt="CAFE+RACER+MOTO+(glen+allsop)+010" width="2000" height="1333" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Unknown.jpeg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-742" src="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Unknown-2400x1600.jpeg" alt="Unknown" width="2400" height="1600" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/CAFE-RACER-MOTO-glen-allsop-011.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-738" src="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/CAFE-RACER-MOTO-glen-allsop-011.jpg" alt="CAFE+RACER+MOTO+(glen+allsop)+011" width="2000" height="1333" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: cent