(1172, 158, '2016-02-24 15:25:29', '2016-02-24 15:25:29', '<img class="alignleft wp-image-1180 size-thumbnail" src="https://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Conquer-The-East-Carbon-Fiber-Sunglasses-7-of-11-2400x1600.jpg" alt="" width="2400" height="1600" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="medium body-copy">\r\n<div class="block-content dynamic-text-left">\r\n<h2>CONQUER THE EAST</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span class="drop-cap">L</span>ife unstaged. That''s what we are always preaching at DIROCCO. It''s a simple concept. Instead of looking toward others and being fascinated by what they are pretending to do, we encourage others to actually do it. Conquer The East is an experience that lives at the core of this concept. As our founders pilgrimed their Ducati Sport Classics from Miami to NYC, they share the story and what embodying this philosophy entails.\r\n\r\n<strong>What was the purpose of Conquer The East?</strong>\r\n\r\nExactly that. At least in our minds. It was about the journey, not the destination. We rode for about seven days; taking our time to visit and wander into different spots. It''s a lot of time considering the distance was only about 1300 miles.\r\n\r\n<strong>What were some of those spots?</strong>\r\n\r\nWe had a lot of intermediate spots in small towns but the checkpoints were Savannah, Charleston, Florence, Washington D.C., Baltimore, and finally NYC.\r\n\r\n<strong>Did you catch any rain?</strong>\r\n\r\nLoads of it. But we powered through. We were completely drenched for over half of the trip. Looking back on it, it made us connect with our bikes at a deeper level.\r\n\r\n<strong>Outside of your helmets, what piece of gear was essential to Conquer The East?</strong>\r\n\r\nThat''s a tough question! I''d like to say our Belstaff jackets because they were waxed so they helped immensely when we got hit in the rain. Truthfully though, when you''re riding long distance the Sun and the concrete are really tough on your eyes. So our shades were instrumental to easing the strain on our eyes in both sun and rain.\r\n\r\n<strong>What''s the goal here?</strong>\r\n\r\nPeople out there are living their lives aspiring to pictures and media they see that are actually just production sets with models pretending to do these things. We want to hopefully encourage others to just do what they are aching to do. It doesn''t take much more than the will to do it. We are all capable of the same things.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignleft wp-image-1182 size-thumbnail" src="https://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Conquer-The-East-Carbon-Fiber-Sunglasses-9-of-11-2400x1600.jpg" alt="" width="2400" height="1600" /></p>\r\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignleft wp-image-1175 size-thumbnail" src="https://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Conquer-The-East-Carbon-Fiber-Sunglasses-2-of-11-2400x1600.jpg" alt="" width="2400" height="1600" /></p>\r\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignleft wp-image-1179 size-thumbnail" src="https://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Conquer-The-East-Carbon-Fiber-Sunglasses-6-of-11-1624x2000.jpg" alt="" width="1624" height="2000" /></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-1176" src="https://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Conquer-The-East-Carbon-Fiber-Sunglasses-3-of-11-1333x2000.jpg" alt="Conquer-The-East-Carbon-Fiber-Sunglasses-(3-of-11)" width="1333" height="2000" />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-1183" src="https://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Conquer-The-East-Carbon-Fiber-Sunglasses-10-of-11-2400x1600.jpg" alt="Conquer-The-East-Carbon-Fiber-Sunglasses-(10-of-11)" width="2400" height="1600" /><a href="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/product/tatano/">Explore the TATANO frame</a><img class="aligncenter wp-image-442 size-full" src="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/TATANO_FRONT.jpg" alt="TATANO_FRONT" width="2400" height="2000" /></p>', 'The East', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-east', '', '', '2016-02-24 17:40:24', '2016-02-24 17:40:24', '', 0, 'https://www.diroccoeyewear.com/?p=1172', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1173, 161, '2016-02-24 15:25:49', '2016-02-24 15:25:49', '<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-740" src="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/CAFE-RACER-MOTO-glen-allsop-013.jpg" alt="CAFE+RACER+MOTO+(glen+allsop)+013" width="2000" height="1334" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="medium body-copy">\r\n<div class="block-content dynamic-text-left">\r\n<h2>MR. ROSS PINO &amp; HIS MANY BIKES</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span class="drop-cap">M</span>r. Ross Pino is by far and away the real deal. As a model/actor he''s constantly used in photoshoots by brands who are looking to buy his look/story. He''s one of those men out there who is far from being a faker, and so, is why we are sharing his long journeyed story on our featured storytellers section.\r\n\r\nThe pictures were taken by photographer @GlenAllsop\r\n\r\n<strong>We know how much love you have for riding. As not only an actor/model but also a father, is there a time limit as to when you''ll stop riding?</strong>\r\n\r\nI don''t think I''ll ever stop riding. I''ve had 5 bikes and I''ve built every single one of them. It does get harder to find the time with the different loves I have in my life now but for me it''s therapy, so I don''t see it going anywhere.\r\n\r\n<strong>What''s your favorite thing about older bikes vs newer production bikes?</strong>\r\n\r\nThere''s something inherently beautiful about a carburator. Its imperfection and inexactitude give the bike a soul.\r\n\r\n<strong>What''s the one thing you can''t ride without?</strong>\r\n\r\nI think eye protection is extremely important when riding. A helmet will save you from an accident but a good pair of shades will save you from getting <em>into</em> one... water, bugs, sun glare. I''ve never had a pair of frames which I''ve felt more comfortable driving in than the TATANO. They''ll never fly off my face.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-737" src="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/CAFE-RACER-MOTO-glen-allsop-010.jpg" alt="CAFE+RACER+MOTO+(glen+allsop)+010" width="2000" height="1333" /></p>\r\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-742" src="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Unknown-2400x1600.jpeg" alt="Unknown" width="2400" height="1600" /></p>\r\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-738" src="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/CAFE-RACER-MOTO-glen-allsop-011.jpg" alt="CAFE+RACER+MOTO+(glen+allsop)+011" width="2000" height="1333" /></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/product/tatano/">Explore the TATANO frame</a></span><img class="aligncenter wp-image-442 size-full" src="http://www.diroccoeyewear.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/TATANO_FRONT.jpg" alt="TATANO_FRONT" width="2400" height="2000" /></p>', 'CONQUER', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1172-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-24 15:25:49', '2016-02-24 15:25:49', '', 1172, 'https://www.diroccoeyewear.com/1172-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
